init_text: Following World War III, all the nations of the world agreed to 50 years of strict isolation from one another in order to prevent additional conflicts. 50 years later, the United States comes out of exile, only to learn that no one else went into isolation.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: by the Russians to take over the world.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Italians have been working on this plan for a while.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The United States, being the only nation to come out of isolation, was the only nation that could stop the Italians.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This made the Italians realize they had a fight on their hands.
